{"name":"Mathlib.Algebra.GroupWithZero.Defs","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Algebra.Group.Defs"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Defs.lean#L21-L24","name":"GroupWithZero","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Defs.html#GroupWithZero","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Defs.lean#L16-L16","name":"MonoidWithZero","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Defs.html#MonoidWithZero","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Defs.lean#L14-L14","name":"MulZeroOneClass","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Defs.html#MulZeroOneClass","doc":"A typeclass for non-associative monoids with zero elements. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Defs.lean#L11-L11","name":"SemigroupWithZero","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Defs.html#SemigroupWithZero","doc":"A type `S₀` is a \"semigroup with zero” if it is a semigroup with zero element, and `0` is left\nand right absorbing. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Defs.lean#L5-L7","name":"MulZeroClass","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Defs.html#MulZeroClass","doc":"Typeclass for expressing that a type `M₀` with multiplication and a zero satisfies\n`0 * a = 0` and `a * 0 = 0` for all `a : M₀`. "}]}